lead_paragraph: America still' adds to her laurels in England. In addition to making the fastest yachts, the best plough, the most serviceable reaping ma chines, , , She can now boast of outdoing the-world in picking locks. The distinction is of somewhat questionable character; generally the persons who have been most expert at thisbusiness, have not enjoyed in the highest degree.
